The Police has assured residents of Zonkwa in Zangon Kataf Local Government, Kaduna State that it was doing everything possible to halt frequent theft of motorcycles in the area. The Divisional Police Officer in the area, ASP Sunday Dangana gave the assurance in an interview with the News Agency of Nigeria (NAN) on Wednesday in Zonkwa. He said that the police has taken appropriate measures to track and apprehend the perpetrators. Do you have something awesome to share with the world? Click here to share Do you ever have any question about anything you wish to ask and get answer? Click here to ask Follow us on twitter @NigeriaTodayNG Also, Like us on facebook This post was syndicated from The NEWS. Click here to read the full text on the original website.